<h3>FOLDING GLASS WALLS</h3>
<a href="https://solarinnovations.com/our-products/aluminum-doors/folding-glass-walls/">Folding Glass Walls</a>Â can open during favorable weather to provide an unobstructed view of sporting events. These accordion style doors can then be closed at times of harsher weather, providing a barrier between spectators and the elements outside. The doors are thermally broken, allowing fans to view games from a comfortable, temperature controlled environment. Operable swing doors can also be incorporated into folding glass walls to provide an entryway that does not require the entire wall to be opened.

