<h3>SLIDE &amp; STACKING GLASS WALLS</h3>
Slide and Stacking Glass Walls consist of individual panels that slide on a track one-by-one and stack parallel or perpendicular with the wall to provide an unobstructed view for spectators. Slide and stacking glass walls can also incorporate swing doors to create an independent entryway when the system is closed during harsh weather. The framing of Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup>â€™ stacking glass walls is constructed from low maintenance aluminum, which does not rot, warp, or rust, ensuring longevity and fewer repairs.

