<h3>CLEAR GLASS WALLS</h3>
Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup>Â can engineer clear glass walls for exterior and interior uses, making it an ideal product for stadium suites. The exposed glass offers unobstructed views because the vertical sides of the operable walls feature exposed glass without any metal framing. This allow consumers to get a great view without having to expose themselves to the harsh elements of the inner field. Glass to glass options provide clear views while adding gaskets will increase thermal performance.

<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-39182" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/stadium-clear-glass-walls.jpg" alt="" width="1344" height="648" />
